      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need help writing an email to a customer. They bought this really expensive espresso machine from us, but the shipping is like two weeks late because of some mistake in our logistics department. I need to apologize and tell them what happened without sounding like a mess. Can you help me draft something?",
